===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{label|en|uncountable}} A mixture of [[lime]] or [[cement]], [[sand]] and [[water]] used for [[bonding]] [[building block]]s.
# {{label|en|countable|military}} A muzzle-loading, [[indirect]] fire [[weapon]] with a tube length of 10 to 20 [[caliber]]s and designed to lob [[shell]]s at very steep [[trajectories]].
# {{label|en|countable}} A hollow [[vessel]] used to [[pound]], [[crush]], [[rub]], [[grind]] or [[mix]] [[ingredient]]s with a [[pestle]].

